[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Here's the full pipeline assembled into a single function. In production, this would be orchestrated by EventBridge Scheduler triggering a Step Functions workflow (Glue for feature assembly and trajectory computation, SageMaker for scoring, Lambda for detection and routing). Here we run it sequentially for clarity.
